Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.69,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(1578,622)}游佐茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.69,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord2\fs35\pos(1029,464)}山梨县北杜市，三得利白州蒸馏所所在地。
