Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.23,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord2\fs35\pos(138,787)}岐阜县郡上市，辰巳蒸馏所所在地。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.16,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur5\fs100\pos(960,331)}上伊那 牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.16,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur5\bord2\fs35\pos(960,684)}长野县上伊那郡，本坊酒造驹岳蒸馏所所在地。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.37,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur5\fs100\pos(960,331)}砺波　伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.37,OP_Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur5\bord2\fs35\pos(960,684)}富山县砺波市，若鹤酒造三郎丸蒸馏所所在地。
